<div id="sospc-widget" class="sospc-closed">
  <div id="sospc-fab-content">
    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg>
    <span id="sospc-fab-text">Diagnostic PC</span>
    <span id="sospc-fab-badge" style="display:none">!</span>
  </div>
  <div id="sospc-panel-content">
    <div id="sospc-header">
      <div>
        <span id="sospc-header-title">Assistant SOS-PC</span>
        <span id="sospc-header-sub">Diagnostic intelligent</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;">
        <button id="sospc-reset-btn" onclick="sospcReset()" title="Nouveau scan">
          <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"></polyline><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 .49-4.5"></path></svg>
          Nouveau scan
        </button>
        <button id="sospc-close-btn" onclick="sospcToggle()" aria-label="Fermer">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="sospc-view-waiting">
      <div id="sospc-waiting-body">
        <p id="sospc-intro-title">Analysez votre PC gratuitement</p>
        <p id="sospc-intro-desc">Notre IA détecte les problèmes de performance, les erreurs système et vous donne des conseils personnalisés.</p>
        <div id="sospc-steps">
          <div class="sospc-step"><span class="sospc-step-n">1</span><span>Ouvrez le Terminal (<kbd>Win</kbd>+<kbd>X</kbd> → Terminal)</span></div>
          <div class="sospc-step"><span class="sospc-step-n">2</span><span>Copiez et collez cette commande :</span></div>
        </div>
        <div id="sospc-cmd-box">
          <code id="sospc-cmd">chargement...</code>
          <button id="sospc-copy-btn" onclick="sospcCopy()">Copier</button>
        </div>
        <div class="sospc-step"><span class="sospc-step-n">3</span><span>Restez sur cette page — le diagnostic apparaîtra automatiquement ici !</span></div>
        <div id="sospc-waiting-indicator" style="display:none;"><div id="sospc-pulse"></div><span>En attente des données...</span></div>
        <p id="sospc-privacy">🔒 Aucun fichier personnel collecté.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="sospc-view-diag" style="display:none;">
      <div id="sospc-score-wrap">
        <span id="sospc-score-lbl">Santé du PC</span>
        <div id="sospc-score-track"><div id="sospc-score-fill"></div></div>
        <span id="sospc-score-val">—</span>
      </div>
      <div id="sospc-messages"></div>
      <div id="sospc-suggestions"></div>
      <div id="sospc-attach-bar" style="display:none;">
        <button id="sospc-attach-btn" onclick="sospcAttachToForm()">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.44 11.05l-9.19 9.19a6 6 0 0 1-8.49-8.49l9.19-9.19a4 4 0 0 1 5.66 5.66l-9.2 9.19a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l8.49-8.48"></path></svg>
          Joindre au formulaire de contact
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="sospc-input-wrap">
        <input id="sospc-input" type="text" placeholder="Posez une question..." onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')sospcSend()" />
        <button id="sospc-send" onclick="sospcSend()">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
